OL,4,Cat chip shop worker
OL,6,FChip shop staff have described the
OL,7,Fmoment a gunman threatened to kill a
OL,8,Fworker during an armed robbery.
OL,10,FCCTV footage shows the moment the
OL,11,Fmasked man pointed the weapon at a
OL,12,Fstaff member's head at Ocean Fish and
OL,13,FGrill in Leicester, before fleeing
OL,14,Fwith the till.
OL,16,FWitnesses said the gunman entered the
OL,17,Fshop in Swinford Avenue, Eyres
OL,18,FMonsell, at around 7.30pm on Saturday
OL,19,F8th March, wearing a balaclava, black
OL,20,Fgloves and a tracksuit.
