OL,6,FManager Yaren Tunc, who's 20,
OL,7,Fdescribed the moment she ran for
OL,8,Fsafety after spotting the gun.
OL,10,F"I was in there with the other worker
OL,11,Fwho is 65.
OL,13,F"I saw the gun and then ran out the
OL,14,Fback, but it was really scary. All you
OL,15,Fthink about is your life and if you're
OL,16,Fgoing to die or not. My life flashed
OL,17,Fbefore my eyes."
OL,19,FYaren said the armed man told a staff
OL,20,Fmember he was "going to kill him" if
OL,21,Fhe did not hand over money.
