OL,6,FWhen the worker did not immediately
OL,7,Fcomply, the robber grabbed the till
OL,8,Fand fled.
OL,10,FShe said the worker was "really
OL,11,Fscared".
OL,13,FYaren dialled 999 from the back of the
OL,14,Fshop, and armed police arrived five
OL,15,Fminutes later. She said:
OL,17,F"I've not been in since that day. Had
OL,18,Fnightmares every day. Couldn't go
OL,19,Fsleep".
