OL,4,Cat chip shop worker
OL,6,F"My dad is currently in the (family-
OL,7,Fowned) shop and it's nerve-racking
OL,8,Fbecause you never know if they might
OL,9,Fcome again."
OL,11,FA Leicestershire Police spokesman said
OL,12,Fno arrests have been made, and
OL,13,Fofficers are investigating.
OL,15,FThey said: "It was reported that just
OL,16,Fafter 7.30pm a man went into the
OL,17,Fpremises and threatened staff with
OL,18,Fwhat was believed to be a handgun,
OL,19,Fbefore taking a cash register.
